00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:21.279
equivariant.

00:11:18.720 --> 00:11:24.320
The entire computation is parallel,

00:11:21.279 --> 00:11:27.920
right? And all positions can compute

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:30.399
their attention simultaneously.

00:11:27.920 --> 00:11:32.560
Uh this is all to all connection. every

00:11:30.399 --> 00:11:35.760
position can directly attend to every

00:11:32.560 --> 00:11:38.880
other position in one step. So, uh none

00:11:35.760 --> 00:11:42.200
of those matrices wk

00:11:38.880 --> 00:11:42.200
and w

00:11:42.560 --> 00:11:48.800
depend on the sequence lengths. That

00:11:44.800 --> 00:11:51.200
means that the same wq wk and wv works

00:11:48.800 --> 00:11:54.800
for any n.

00:11:51.200 --> 00:11:58.000
Okay, which is very significant.

00:11:54.800 --> 00:12:01.040
Okay, so the there are some nice

00:11:58.000 --> 00:12:04.480
computation aspects, right? But there is

00:12:01.040 --> 00:12:06.959
a problem here and

00:12:04.480 --> 00:12:11.360
the problem is where did the sequence

00:12:06.959 --> 00:12:16.000
